The paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for condition monitoring, specifically dictionary learning. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves signal processing and analysis, which could fall under the categories of signal processing (cs.SD) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses the application of these techniques to improve overall equipment effectiveness, which could fall under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
